      "text": "Ulrich, 10th Prince Kinsky of Wchinitz and Tettau\nUlrich, 10th Prince Kinsky of Wchinitz and Tettau (; 15 August 189319 December 1938) was the titular pretender Prince Kinsky of Wchinitz and Tettau.",
