      "score": 0.07184013296771596,
      "text": "The FBI Story\nThe FBI Story is a 1959 American drama film starring James Stewart, and produced and directed by Mervyn LeRoy. The screenplay by Richard L. Breen and John Twist is based on a book by Don Whitehead.",
      "score_breakdown": {
