      "score": 0.04281744687114648,
      "text": "Jean-Marie Cavada\nJean-Marie Cavada (born 24 February 1940 in Épinal, Vosges) is a French politician who served as a Member of the European Parliament for Ile de France from 2004 until 2019. Since 3 December 2011 he is president of the European Movement France.",
      "score_breakdown": {
