      "title": "Louise Élisabeth d'Orléans",
      "score": 0.042259911105502285,
      "text": "Louise Élisabeth d'Orléans\nLouise Élisabeth d'Orléans was one of the seven daughters of Philippe II, Duke of Orléans, and his wife, Françoise Marie de Bourbon. Her mother was a legitimised daughter of Louis XIV of France and his mistress, Madame de Montespan. She was known as Élisabeth. As a member of the reigning House of Bourbon, Élisabeth was a \"princesse du sang\".",
